args: Damn it! They just keep comin'!
We have more this way, as well!
Did that knight over there just\nsummon lightning?
We're fine. Thank you for saving us.
Still, it is dangerous here.\nYou should take your leave.
Curses! I missed a few!\nMy apologies—leave this to me.
We won't let you fight alone.\nDragon, I invoke thee!
Pick yer jaw up off the dirt and start\nfightin' these fiends already!
...That appears to be the last of them.\nEverything should be well now.
Thank you again for your help.
I don't know what would have happened\nif you hadn't come along.
It is I who should be thanking you.\nThat second wave of fiends might\nhave been too much for me.
We ain't the types to turn our backs\non someone in need.
By Ilia! The Thunderswift Lord himself?!
There are some who call me by that name.
Er, should I know this Thunderswift Lord?
He leads the Knights of Levin who protect\na kingdom of the same name to the north.

He can bend lightning to his will,
and has used it to save the kingdom
from peril many a time—which is why
he's known as Levin's Champion.
So what's this cat doin' here?
Forgive me for speaking out of turn,\nbut might I ask your power?
I pray I'm mistaken, but is such a power\nrelated to the seeds of the abyss?
The seeds of the abyss?\nThat's not a name I've heard before.
They're a kind of fiend that absorbs\npeople in order to grow larger.
I came to this continent in\nsearch of one of them.
I don't think my shapeshifting has any\nconnection to that. Mine is a power\nof dragons.
Hey! Don't just show up and start\naccusing people of weird fiend junk!
I know this guy, and he'd NEVER\nuse a power like that!
I apologize if I have offended you,\nbut the power is truly dangerous.
So long as the slightest doubt exists\nin my mind, I must act.
I feel as though we are\ngoing around in circles.
No need to yell! We're right here.
Why don't you come with us until you're\nconvinced we're telling the truth?

Look, I know ya love everybody and all
that noise, but are we really gonna let
some guy what thinks ya have evil
powers pal around with us?!
If he suspects me, nothing we say\nhere will change that.
The fastest way to convince him of my\ninnocence is for him to experience more\nshapeshifting first-hand.
If you are proposing this for true,\nI accept.
Then let's head back to our castle.
Don't be so harsh on him, Notte.\nThis is just how he is.
I still don't like anything about this.\nWhat if he gets up to funny business?\nOr monkeyshines?!
Then we will simply ensure His Highness\nis kept safe.
Yeah, I still don't like it.
Regardless, we should get moving before\nthe two of them leave us behind.
